Navigating and Working with Files 
mkdir			//make directory (folder)
rmdir			//remove dir
touch 			//how to create a file
cp			//copy a file
rm			//remove file or dir
mv			//copy, rename and delete the original.



How to count the number of files exlcuding the subdirectories (i.e. excluding folders)?
ls -F |grep -v / | wc -l

grep -v 		//invert matching
__________________________________________________________________________________________

